3 things you should look for in a Realtor 👇

1. Tells it like it is:

Go for an agent who tells it like it is, with no sugar-coating. They should share all the need-to-know info about a property or deal, so there are no ugly surprises down the line. A quick look at reviews or a chat with their past clients can give a good sense of whether they play it straight.

2.Good Word of Mouth:

A solid rep goes a long way. Ask the agent for some references or dive into online reviews to see what people are saying. If they’ve left a trail of happy clients, that’s a good sign!

3. Keeping in Touch:

Pick an agent who’s good at keeping the lines of communication open. They should be easy to get a hold of and quick to fill you in on the latest updates. The last thing anyone wants is to be left in the dark, especially when it comes to big decisions like buying or selling a house.
